<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>28</hymn_number>
<author>Matt. 10</author>
<title>THY WILL BE DONE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Pa, Ka Pathien, In apat,
 Gamla taka ka um laiin;
 Lunggil a ti di'n ei hilh in,
 &quot;Nang thu hi hen!&quot;

[V2]
 2. Guol lungtuolte ka gamla tieng,
 Lungkham, thawmhau in um mahleng;
 Nanga kipie'n zie gen zing ka,
 &quot;Nang thu hi hen!&quot;

[V3]
 3. Ka lunggil lungkham tak ahin,
 Na tha zintung in, hihnuom hen;
 Adang cheng chu Nangah ka nga'i,
 &quot;Nang thu hi hen!&quot;

[V4]
 4. Ka utna nicheng' hihhat in,
 Nang deih thilbawl utna ei pie'n;
 Tih haksatna cheng la mang in,
 &quot;Nang thu hi hen!&quot;

[V5]
 5. Mitthi puma ka pauchamna,
 Leh ka hinna hung beih tieng;
 Luigal nuomzaw ah la sa'ng ie,
 &quot;Nang thu hi hen!&quot;</lyrics>
</song>